{"tid":1895174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共稍後會見傳媒 消息指正考慮派包機接回湖北港人","createTime":"2020-02-24T11:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:33:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b991606572ac289221b817cc9ca4d8f5e194e67","tid":1895174,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"聶德權李家超陳肇始稍後會見傳媒<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權、保安局局長李家超和食物及衞生局局長陳肇始，稍後在政府總部會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n消息說，政府正考慮是否用包機接載滯留在湖北及武漢的港人返港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266835&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1266835%26csid%3D261_341&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=e0f8990f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266835&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}